This map is the best most realistic map i have made. Its the sequal of gg_eagleye. Its set in a city....when winter is oppon them. There is moving clouds thunder with real lighting...water barrals, crates, places to hide behind and the game play is awsome.....
I have also put a lot of time into optimzing it so there isnt has much lag..if your still having problems please tell me via PM.
Pictures are a bit dark but i cant really help that!
Please comment and rate!
